		<para id="eip-553">
    Find the equation for a parabola whose vertex is <m:math><m:mi>(3,−1)</m:mi></m:math>, and that contains the point <m:math><m:mi>(0,4)</m:mi></m:math>.
  </para>
	</problem>
</exercise><exercise id="element-495"><problem id="id5558683">
